\details{
This package fits a Bayesian multilevel model for repeatedly measured areal
spatial data under the Leroux conditional autoregressive (CAR) prior and its
nonspatial counterpart, and computes a closed-form replication threshold
\eqn{m^*} beyond which the two models yield effectively equivalent posterior
inference for regression coefficients.
}
